*   Martha Jefferson ('Patsy') Randolph (1817–1857)
*   Mary Buchanan Randolph (1818–1821)
*   Careyanne Nicholas Randolph (1820–1857)
*   Mary Buchanan Randolph (1821–1884)
*   Ellen Wayles Randolph (1823–1896)
